Package: baesql
Architecture: arm64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Experimental independent relational database management system
 BaeSQL is an experimental independent relational database management system.
 It stores data in custom .bae files and does not wrap another database engine.
